 steps 5


1.Configure the dispatcher servlet(front controller) in web.xml

2.Create Spring Configuration File - where we declare our beans

3.Configure View Resolver (declare as bean in spring config)

4.Create Controller ( works as back end controller)

5.Create a View to show(page)

